FBIS3-23391 "jptot013__l94072" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 24 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Kakh Activist Sentenced To 6 Months Imprisonment TA2403150094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1400 GMT 24 Mar 94 TA2403150094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The Jerusalem Magistrate's Court has meted out a six month prison sentence to Tiran Pollak, a member of Kakh's Committee for Security on the Roads. Pollak was convicted of assault, disturbing a policeman, and rioting. Our police affairs correspondent Aviv Bushinsky reports the judge acquiesced to Pollak's request to incarcerate him only after the Passover holiday.
